title: Celebrity Gossip Part 2 - Netflix Is Trying
description: The Grammy awards are coming up but before nominations are out, we’re finding out about a few artists that basically said “thanks but no thanks”.... Plus, Netflix is changing up their subscription plans in hopes to keep customers.
